data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! Nestled in a quiet community in Stony Point Commons, this beautiful townhome is just minutes to downtown and accessible to tons of retail shopping, restaurants and recreational activities.  With more than 2100 square feet of living space, this like NEW townhome is loaded with options - LVP flooring, a white kitchen with upgraded cabinetry and molding, stainless steel hood with smooth top cooking, tiled backsplash and an oversized quartz island with seating to accommodate four to six people.  The open floor plan is flooded with natural light with seamless transitions from the kitchen to the dining space and living room.  The living room has patio doors that lead to a large exterior deck overlooking a natural wooded setting.  On the third floor, there are three bedrooms including a primary suite with private bath and a large walk-in closet.  The ground level has another bedroom complete with a private bath and access to a walkout area in the backyard.  Motivated seller - now offering $10K in closing costs.  Schedule your showing today!
